{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"95ab3498-a110-42cb-95e8-d9f4dd503b4c","content":"In MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are **no longer supported**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's how to migrate your three configuration items:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` property | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` |\n| Code coverage DataCollector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` |\n\nLet me create the equivalent `.runsettings` file and update your project:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_V16iXD9b38ihW4ua2Q355t","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_1tecL5phxVVQUup7WyC89L","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-2dd8a9b21a154dce9b9bff91210c2140/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.VanguardCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-2dd8a9b21a154dce9b9bff91210c2140/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_AR5ZZ2B3XR4F4MaKjiUZDD","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-2dd8a9b21a154dce9b9bff91210c2140/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.8.0\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>","new_str":"<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n    <RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\local.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n  <ItemGroup>\n    <PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.8.0\" />\n  </ItemGroup>\n</Project>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-2dd8a9b21a154dce9b9bff91210c2140/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"13dc5019-744f-483e-95db-b7a1c99ba99f","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Test deployment/assembly resolution configuration\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The configuration needs to be migrated to a `.runsettings` file and/or MSTest attributes/properties.\n\nLet me explain how to migrate each piece:\n\n1. **Test timeout** → Use `[Timeout]` attribute on test methods, or set a default timeout in `.runsettings` under `<MSTest><TestTimeout>`.\n\n\n2. **Code coverage data collector** → Configure in `.runsettings` under `<DataCollectionRunSettings>`.\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment** → MSTest v3 handles deployment differently; the `<DeploymentItem>` attribute or `<MSTest><DeploymentEnabled>` in `.runsettings` replaces this.\n\nI need to create a `.runsettings` file that handles all three configurations and update the `.csproj` to reference it instead.","outputTokens":1040,"requestId":"63CB:2B8468:3F1F779:453E8C7:6A02FA4B"},"id":"9794fde2-23a9-4977-896f-7c8482c03c78","timestamp":"2026-05-12T10:01:03.495Z","parentId":"e74779d6-74d7-4e6c-9e84-0c5bc925db05"}
